sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Client as MCP Client (Python)
    participant Ollama as Ollama API
    participant Server as MCP Server
    
    User->>Client: Start client.py
    Client->>Server: Initialize connection
    Server->>Client: Return available tools
    Client->>User: Display available tools
    
    User->>Client: Enter math problem (e.g., "What is 3+2?")
    Client->>Ollama: Call API with prompt and available tools
    Ollama->>Client: Return response with tool call
    
    Note over Client: Extract tool call parameters
    Note over Client: Convert from x,y to a,b if needed
    
    Client->>Server: Call add_numbers tool
    Server->>Server: Execute calculation
    Server->>Client: Return calculation result
    Client->>User: Display result ("The sum of 3 and 2 is 5")